WEBVTT

01:31.425 --> 01:34.428
That's a beautiful pig.

01:34.511 --> 01:38.140
Only the best, Father.

01:39.516 --> 01:41.184
This way, Father.

02:01.580 --> 02:03.457
The boy is showing

02:03.540 --> 02:06.668
all the classical signs of possession,
Father Amorth.

02:07.627 --> 02:09.755
Has the family consulted a doctor?

02:10.339 --> 02:12.966
Many, many doctors.

02:14.092 --> 02:17.137
What are the signs of possession?

02:17.721 --> 02:19.139
He converses in English, Father.

02:20.849 --> 02:23.226
Has he spoken English before?

02:23.310 --> 02:25.187
Never. Not once before.

02:26.104 --> 02:28.190
Do they own a television?

02:28.940 --> 02:30.150
Yes, I believe so.

02:31.943 --> 02:33.487
Okay, thank you.

02:39.951 --> 02:41.203
Ah...

02:41.286 --> 02:43.330
What are you drawing?

02:43.413 --> 02:44.623
A bird.

02:46.666 --> 02:50.545
That's good, kid.

02:52.506 --> 02:55.717
I have a very important job for you.

02:59.137 --> 03:00.555
Do you know the Our Father?

03:01.139 --> 03:03.600
- Yes, Father.
- Good.

03:06.853 --> 03:09.648
You can help your brother.

03:09.731 --> 03:15.821
Repeat the Our Father, over and over.

03:16.405 --> 03:21.410
Don't get distracted.
Relentless. Understood?

03:23.286 --> 03:24.663
Yes, Father.

03:25.497 --> 03:26.331
Good.

03:28.083 --> 03:34.423
Our Father, who art in heaven,
hallowed be thy name...

03:39.219 --> 03:40.846
Bring me the pig.

04:03.869 --> 04:06.329
I am legion.

04:08.707 --> 04:10.500
I am Satan.

04:13.253 --> 04:17.090
I am foul-mouthed behemoth.

04:18.717 --> 04:20.635
Difficult to believe.

04:23.680 --> 04:24.890
You doubt me?

04:24.973 --> 04:28.685
If you are Satan, what is my name?

04:31.438 --> 04:33.148
Describe hell.

04:35.650 --> 04:39.112
You will find out soon enough.

04:39.654 --> 04:41.948
Are you avoiding my questions?

04:42.032 --> 04:43.158
You mock me?

04:50.582 --> 04:52.959
Answer me, Satan.

04:55.837 --> 04:58.924
Why possess this boy?

04:59.007 --> 05:01.551
Why not someone more influential?

05:01.635 --> 05:06.431
I can possess anyone I choose.

05:06.848 --> 05:07.682
Ah.

05:08.808 --> 05:11.394
Could you possess Father Gianni?

05:12.479 --> 05:13.605
A bishop?

05:13.688 --> 05:16.483
Anyone! Anything!

05:16.566 --> 05:18.068
I do not believe you.

05:18.151 --> 05:21.571
I don't believe
you could even possess this pig.

05:22.322 --> 05:24.699
Can you do it? You have the power.

05:24.783 --> 05:26.535
Could you possess the pig?

05:26.618 --> 05:28.245
- Yes, I can.
- Come on, Satan.

05:28.328 --> 05:29.162
Watch me!

05:29.246 --> 05:32.207
Possess the pig.
Show me you are the Prince of Darkness.

05:33.959 --> 05:35.335
Show to me your power.

05:35.418 --> 05:36.419
Have you done it?

05:36.503 --> 05:38.380
Have you possessed him, Satan?

05:40.298 --> 05:42.217
Have you possessed it, Satan?

05:53.478 --> 05:54.646
Be calm.

05:55.981 --> 05:58.942
God blesses you.

05:59.025 --> 06:00.694
You can sleep now, my son.

06:00.777 --> 06:02.612
The demon has gone.

06:08.827 --> 06:10.287
<i>God is with you.</i>

06:38.189 --> 06:40.483
<i>♪ Oh, the heads that turn ♪</i>

06:41.693 --> 06:43.862
<i>♪ Make my back burn ♪</i>

06:44.738 --> 06:47.324
<i>♪ And those heads that turn ♪</i>

06:48.450 --> 06:52.495
<i>♪ Make my back, make my back burn... ♪</i>

07:06.009 --> 07:09.554
Amy, we're not in America anymore.
You can't dress like that.

07:11.056 --> 07:11.890
Why?

07:11.973 --> 07:14.601
Because there's gonna be
construction workers everywhere.

07:17.646 --> 07:18.980
How you doing back there?

07:19.689 --> 07:23.652
<i>♪ The world and the world... ♪</i>

07:50.553 --> 07:53.223
So we left everything for this?

07:53.306 --> 07:55.225
Amy, please. Don't start.

07:55.308 --> 07:59.187
- You know exactly what I'm gonna say.
- Yes, and I don't wanna hear it.

08:00.980 --> 08:02.982
What do you think? Pretty cool, huh?

08:05.610 --> 08:06.903
Yeah, I know.

08:16.830 --> 08:17.706
Cuckoo!

08:25.255 --> 08:27.507
Ah... Gabriele.

08:29.884 --> 08:32.762
Why do you think Saint Michael

08:32.846 --> 08:35.515
didn't kill Satan when he had the chance?

08:36.182 --> 08:38.893
That is a question of theology.

08:41.146 --> 08:42.355
No shit.

08:42.439 --> 08:46.735
Perhaps it was his mercy
that stayed Saint Michael's sword.

08:46.818 --> 08:49.404
The only thing that arrests God's love

08:50.155 --> 08:52.449
is a person's freedom to choose.

08:53.074 --> 08:57.996
But God cannot be God
unless he allows for this choice

08:58.079 --> 08:59.706
even for the damned.

09:00.290 --> 09:01.833
Saint Michael, he knows this.

09:03.293 --> 09:06.129
We will all be judged.

09:06.212 --> 09:07.630
We will all be judged

09:08.423 --> 09:10.216
by how much we love.

09:10.300 --> 09:11.426
Hm.

09:11.509 --> 09:13.470
Do not worry, Gabriele.

09:14.262 --> 09:16.890
I will defend you.

09:16.973 --> 09:18.141
Defend me?

09:18.224 --> 09:19.476
Mm.

09:21.352 --> 09:22.479
My faith

09:23.229 --> 09:24.981
does not require defense.

09:31.029 --> 09:31.946
Oh-ho!

09:33.031 --> 09:34.157
Wow.

09:34.240 --> 09:37.076
- What do you think, guys?
- Cozy.

09:37.160 --> 09:40.538
Oh, come on.
Give it a chance. This is awesome.

09:41.456 --> 09:44.000
- Señora Vasquez.
- Carlos, hi!

09:44.083 --> 09:45.794
So nice to put a face to the voice.

09:46.503 --> 09:47.337
Um...

09:47.796 --> 09:50.215
<i>Padre--</i> Father Esquibel...

09:50.298 --> 09:52.926
- Pleasure to meet you, Miss Vasquez.
- Uh, Julia, please.

09:53.009 --> 09:55.595
- Carlos was giving me a tour.
- Oh, great.

09:55.678 --> 09:59.098
I just wanted to stop by and welcome
you and your family to the diocese.

09:59.182 --> 10:01.476
- I'm sorry.
- Oh, no, no, no, please. Go for it.

10:01.559 --> 10:03.353
I'm glad to see you made it safe.

10:04.062 --> 10:05.814
All right. Go find your room, twerp.

10:11.903 --> 10:13.988
Hey. Can I get one of those?

10:14.072 --> 10:15.240
Yes, of course.

10:15.323 --> 10:17.575
This property has been in disrepair

10:17.659 --> 10:19.452
- for as long as I can remember.
- Thank you.

10:19.536 --> 10:23.206
So it's a wonderful thing you're doing,
restoring the abbey.

10:23.289 --> 10:25.959
We are being very respectful
of the existing architecture.

10:26.042 --> 10:28.920
This has actually been
in my husband's family for generations,

10:29.003 --> 10:30.547
and we just inherited it.

10:30.630 --> 10:32.632
Is Mr. Vasquez here or--?

10:32.715 --> 10:36.386
Oh, uh, he passed, actually.
About a year ago.

10:36.469 --> 10:38.638
- I'm sorry for your loss.
- It's okay.

10:38.721 --> 10:42.392
If you need anything,
please, hm, don't hesitate.

10:42.475 --> 10:43.351
Okay.

10:43.935 --> 10:45.687
I will remember him in my prayers.

10:45.770 --> 10:48.565
Oh, that's very kind of you.
Thank you. It was nice to meet you.

10:49.065 --> 10:51.401
Okay, Carlos, talk to me.
What's up? Where are we at?

10:51.484 --> 10:53.611
The basement excavation
is very complicated.

10:53.695 --> 10:54.988
More expensive, you mean?

10:55.071 --> 10:56.739
- I'm afraid so.
- All right.

10:56.823 --> 10:58.241
I'll take another look at the plans.

10:58.324 --> 11:01.202
If you could just show me what the
basement looks like, maybe I can wire--

11:01.286 --> 11:04.414
Amy, get off of there
before you break your neck.

11:04.497 --> 11:07.417
Is that a cigarette?
Put that out right now, please.

11:07.500 --> 11:09.085
- Fine.
- No! Oh, my God.

11:45.872 --> 11:46.789
Cute.

11:47.290 --> 11:48.499
Get out of my room.

12:04.015 --> 12:06.809
<i>♪ Beautiful girl, lovely dress ♪</i>

12:06.893 --> 12:09.479
<i>♪ Where she is now, I can only guess ♪</i>

12:09.562 --> 12:12.440
<i>♪ 'Cause it's gone, daddy, gone
The love is gone ♪</i>

12:12.523 --> 12:15.360
<i>♪ Yeah, it's gone, daddy, gone
The love is gone ♪</i>

12:15.443 --> 12:17.445
<i>♪ Yeah, it's gone, daddy, gone... ♪</i>

13:21.426 --> 13:23.094
Hey, have you seen your brother?

13:24.762 --> 13:25.596
Amy.

13:30.810 --> 13:36.107
Look, I really can't handle
the silent treatment from both my kids.

13:37.567 --> 13:40.194
- I know you don't wanna be here.
- Yeah, no shit.

13:40.278 --> 13:41.112
Amy.

13:42.071 --> 13:44.699
Please, I need your help.

13:44.782 --> 13:46.826
This abbey is the only thing
your dad left us.

13:46.909 --> 13:48.453
We don't have an income anymore.

13:48.536 --> 13:51.873
Once we fix it up and sell it,
we'll go home. Okay?

13:52.999 --> 13:55.626
Maybe if you could just
at least watch your brother.

13:55.710 --> 13:57.211
Maybe try and get him to talk.

13:57.295 --> 13:59.839
How? He hasn't spoken in almost a year.

14:00.548 --> 14:02.300
Can you try for me?

14:02.383 --> 14:04.302
So you want me to be a mother for you?

14:04.385 --> 14:07.263
Please just keep an eye
on your brother. Okay?

14:14.645 --> 14:16.731
<i>♪ Whoa, whoa ♪</i>

14:16.814 --> 14:20.526
<i>♪ It's a dirty job
But someone's gotta do it ♪</i>

14:25.698 --> 14:28.868
<i>♪ It's a dirty job
But someone's gotta do it ♪</i>

14:28.951 --> 14:30.119
<i>♪ We care a lot ♪</i>

14:32.205 --> 14:33.122
Hold this.

14:40.630 --> 14:43.925
Father Amorth, caffe latte?

14:44.008 --> 14:47.303
At this time of the day? Are you crazy?

14:49.222 --> 14:51.557
Double espresso, Sister.

14:51.641 --> 14:52.809
Thank you.

14:52.892 --> 14:54.102
Sugar?

14:54.185 --> 14:57.522
Sugar is the work of the devil.
No, thank you.

15:01.901 --> 15:02.944
Thank you very much.

15:05.947 --> 15:08.449
Let's get on with this already.

15:09.826 --> 15:11.786
This is a formal hearing.

15:11.869 --> 15:15.039
And as agreed,
proceedings will be undertaken in English.

15:15.123 --> 15:17.917
Ah. All right, let's go.

15:18.000 --> 15:20.837
On the night of June 4th,
in the town of Tropea,

15:21.420 --> 15:23.172
you performed an exorcism

15:23.256 --> 15:26.717
without the approval
of the Reggio Calabria bishop.

15:27.343 --> 15:28.678
It wasn't a--

15:28.761 --> 15:30.304
In English, Father Amorth.

15:32.431 --> 15:35.184
That was not an exorcism.

15:35.268 --> 15:38.938
From Father Gianni's description,
what occurred in Reggio Calabria sounded

15:39.021 --> 15:42.942
exactly like an exorcism,
complete with animal sacrifice, no less.

15:43.025 --> 15:46.070
The boy was maladjusted.
A temporary mental illness.

15:46.154 --> 15:48.865
I use primitive psychology.

15:49.532 --> 15:51.117
The power of suggestion.

15:51.200 --> 15:55.580
You addressed the subject as Satan,
called for him to display his power.

15:56.539 --> 15:58.291
- Do you deny this?
- No.

15:59.125 --> 16:01.669
- That's what I did.
- And why would you do that?

16:01.752 --> 16:03.462
Exorcism is my job,

16:04.005 --> 16:07.091
but the vast majority of the cases
to which I'm assigned

16:07.175 --> 16:09.927
do not require an exorcism.

16:10.636 --> 16:13.389
They just need, uh, a little conversation,

16:14.182 --> 16:16.017
a little understanding,

16:16.100 --> 16:17.518
and sometimes...

16:18.728 --> 16:19.937
a little theater.

16:20.521 --> 16:23.566
Cardinal Sullivan, in my observation,

16:24.108 --> 16:27.320
98% of the cases
that are assigned to Father Amorth

16:27.403 --> 16:30.323
are then further recommended by him

16:30.406 --> 16:32.783
to doctors and psychiatrists.

16:32.867 --> 16:34.327
And the other 2%?

16:35.161 --> 16:36.954
Ah, the other 2%.

16:37.663 --> 16:40.708
This is something
that has confounded all of science

16:40.791 --> 16:43.002
and all of medicine for a very long time.

16:46.088 --> 16:47.381
I call it...

16:48.716 --> 16:49.550
evil.

16:49.634 --> 16:52.970
Your Eminence,
with hundreds of successful exorcisms,

16:53.054 --> 16:57.558
- Father Amorth has been very effective--
- One moment, Bishop Lumumba.

16:58.976 --> 17:01.312
You do raise an interesting point, Amorth.

17:01.896 --> 17:04.982
You are not a doctor,
but these practices of yours

17:05.066 --> 17:07.109
could have damaging effects
on these people.

17:07.777 --> 17:08.778
You are right.

17:09.570 --> 17:10.947
I am not a doctor.

17:11.906 --> 17:13.866
I am not a psychologist.

17:15.326 --> 17:17.536
But I am a theologian, I am a lawyer,

17:17.620 --> 17:20.456
I am a journalist,
and I am a practical man.

17:20.957 --> 17:25.628
I was also a partisan in the war,
so I know a firing squad when I see one.

17:28.839 --> 17:30.383
So, what is this about?

17:30.466 --> 17:32.802
The Congregation
for the Doctrine of the Faith

17:32.885 --> 17:34.470
has recommended to this panel

17:34.971 --> 17:39.892
that the position of chief exorcist
be formally vacated.

17:39.976 --> 17:42.770
So, what you are saying
is that evil does not exist?

17:42.853 --> 17:45.773
The Church is under constant pressure
to sharpen her relevance.

17:45.856 --> 17:48.651
It's time we move past
these outdated beliefs.

17:48.734 --> 17:51.070
Explain to me please, Your Eminence.

17:51.570 --> 17:53.072
If evil does not exist,

17:53.656 --> 17:57.118
what, then, is the role of the Church?

17:58.744 --> 18:02.999
I think we all have to be careful of the
Congregation of the Doctrine of the Faith.

18:03.541 --> 18:06.335
Sounds to me
like they want us all out of a job.

18:11.924 --> 18:14.385
We have more questions for you,
Father Amorth.

18:18.055 --> 18:20.599
How is it that I am suddenly worthy

18:20.683 --> 18:23.311
of the time and attention
of all you powerful men?

18:24.020 --> 18:25.229
I ask you again...

18:26.522 --> 18:27.857
what is this about?

18:27.940 --> 18:29.275
Due process, Father.

18:29.358 --> 18:32.695
So this is not about the dead girl,
Rosaria Velendez,

18:32.778 --> 18:35.614
<i>that I write about
in</i> La Madre di Dio <i>magazine?</i>

18:35.698 --> 18:37.950
What is your due diligence
and process on this?

18:38.034 --> 18:41.037
- Please, cardinal.
- I warn you! I warn you! Father Amorth,

18:41.120 --> 18:42.830
show respect to your superiors.

18:42.913 --> 18:44.290
I do!

18:44.373 --> 18:46.792
I am the chief exorcist of the Vatican.

18:46.876 --> 18:49.795
My position was appointed by my bishop.

18:49.879 --> 18:51.672
My diocese is Rome.

18:51.756 --> 18:53.507
My local bishop is the pope.

18:54.008 --> 18:55.718
If you have a problem with me,

18:56.427 --> 18:58.471
you talk to my boss. Okay?

18:59.347 --> 19:01.390
The pope is infirm.

19:01.474 --> 19:03.392
Father Amorth,
you have not been dismissed.

19:03.476 --> 19:04.977
- Cuckoo.
- Father Amorth!

19:58.823 --> 19:59.657
Hello?

20:01.617 --> 20:02.660
Anyone there?

20:56.213 --> 20:58.632
I can't wait to finish this job.

20:58.716 --> 21:00.009
This place freaks me out.

21:09.518 --> 21:10.436
What is it?

21:13.022 --> 21:15.065
I don't know. Can't see anything.

21:38.672 --> 21:39.924
They hit a gas deposit.

21:40.508 --> 21:44.178
We can't continue working here.
I'm pulling my team from this place.

21:45.262 --> 21:47.348
Come on, let's go. Come on, everybody out.

21:47.431 --> 21:48.265
Wait.

21:49.808 --> 21:50.976
Quick, quick.

22:05.783 --> 22:06.617
Henry?

22:07.243 --> 22:08.661
No. Henry!

22:09.954 --> 22:10.829
Mom!

22:12.289 --> 22:15.209
Oh, my God!
Henry! What is happening?

22:15.292 --> 22:17.211
I don't know,
he was like this when I came in.

22:17.294 --> 22:19.630
Henry? Henry, it's Mommy.

22:19.713 --> 22:20.589
Talk to me.

22:21.757 --> 22:23.926
- Henry.
- Mommy.

22:24.009 --> 22:24.927
He's talking.

22:25.427 --> 22:27.930
- Henry.
- Mommy.

22:33.769 --> 22:35.771
You're all going to die.

22:36.939 --> 22:38.315
Henry! What are you doing?

22:38.399 --> 22:39.733
- Henry! Henry!
- Henry! Henry!

22:51.161 --> 22:53.622
<i>X-rays, blood tests, even the spinal tap</i>

22:53.706 --> 22:56.584
and MRI show no results
of ischemia or hematoma.

22:57.209 --> 22:58.460
What does that mean?

23:02.423 --> 23:06.677
All of his vitals
and brain functions seem to be normal.

23:06.760 --> 23:10.431
Wait, normal? What do you mean?
He was convulsing.

23:12.600 --> 23:14.977
Has he been through any trauma recently?

23:18.022 --> 23:19.523
Um...

23:20.608 --> 23:24.403
Yeah, uh, his dad died about a year ago.

23:27.531 --> 23:29.074
And how did he react?

23:30.117 --> 23:31.118
Uh...

23:31.201 --> 23:32.745
He hasn't spoken since.

23:37.499 --> 23:39.126
Wha-- Psychosis?

23:39.209 --> 23:41.253
No, that's not possible.
He's just a little boy.

23:41.337 --> 23:45.090
Ma'am,
there is nothing that we can do now.

23:45.174 --> 23:48.594
- But he can recommend a good psychiatrist.
- What is this?

23:51.513 --> 23:54.183
If your son continues
trying to hurt himself,

23:54.266 --> 23:56.268
- you can administer him this sedative.
- No.

23:56.852 --> 23:58.145
- Mom.
- I'm so sorry.

23:58.812 --> 23:59.813
Baby.

23:59.897 --> 24:01.106
Oh, my God.

24:08.113 --> 24:10.199
No, I don't think you understand.

24:10.866 --> 24:13.285
But this is an emergency, please.

24:13.369 --> 24:18.499
No, I need to talk to someone
at the consulate who can help me.

24:18.582 --> 24:20.209
I need a specialist.

24:21.794 --> 24:22.628
Okay.

24:24.213 --> 24:25.172
Okay.

24:25.964 --> 24:27.257
Yes, please.

24:48.320 --> 24:49.613
Baby.

24:53.450 --> 24:54.284
Hey.

24:55.494 --> 24:57.621
My love, come here.

25:17.474 --> 25:18.392
Fuck this.

25:25.441 --> 25:27.109
Henry, no.

25:27.192 --> 25:28.610
Henry, stop!

25:28.694 --> 25:30.487
This baby's hungry, you fat cow.

25:30.571 --> 25:32.406
What? What are you saying?

25:32.489 --> 25:34.491
You never breastfed me, Mommy.

25:34.575 --> 25:35.701
- What?
- What the fuck?

25:35.784 --> 25:37.911
Ow!

25:41.707 --> 25:43.208
What the fuck is that?

25:43.292 --> 25:45.878
Bring me the priest.

25:47.212 --> 25:49.089
- Can you help us?
- Yes.

25:50.048 --> 25:51.508
I'm here to help, Julia.

25:51.592 --> 25:52.426
Okay.

26:07.983 --> 26:10.903
Wrong fucking priest!

26:27.544 --> 26:31.048
- Is that you, Gabriele?
- Yes, Holy Father.

26:32.049 --> 26:34.259
They tell me you are sick.

26:34.343 --> 26:36.595
Yes, they hope so.

26:37.471 --> 26:39.348
They wish to see me weak.

26:39.431 --> 26:41.433
But, no, they are.

26:44.937 --> 26:46.605
- Help me.
- Yes.

27:07.668 --> 27:11.213
Perhaps we've done our jobs too well.

27:11.296 --> 27:13.924
Cardinal Sullivan
and the younger generation,

27:14.007 --> 27:17.052
they don't believe in the devil
as we understand it.

27:17.803 --> 27:23.767
It's only an idea for them.
For us, it is very real.

27:24.560 --> 27:26.478
Two hundred fallen angels,

27:26.562 --> 27:30.107
expelled from heaven, driven beneath
the soil where God is not welcomed.

27:31.233 --> 27:33.110
It is not a fairytale.

27:34.236 --> 27:38.073
Your search for truth
is delightful, Gabriele,

27:38.156 --> 27:41.994
but pay attention
to your desire to educate.

27:42.077 --> 27:46.415
Pride manifests itself in different forms.

27:48.041 --> 27:50.419
Pride? Me?

27:53.922 --> 27:56.341
There's a case that needs your attention.

