58:28.922 --> 58:32.384
Did you consider why the demon does this?

58:32.467 --> 58:33.760
To scare us, hm?

58:33.844 --> 58:35.137
For what benefit?

58:35.721 --> 58:36.555
Chaos.

58:38.348 --> 58:39.516
Distraction.

58:39.599 --> 58:41.643
The devil is the great deceiver.

58:41.727 --> 58:43.854
He can make you see things from your past.

58:43.937 --> 58:47.733
Apparitions, memories,
always trying to deceive us.

58:47.816 --> 58:51.528
So we never know what he's thinking,
what he's planning.

58:52.821 --> 58:54.489
If you do not believe me...

58:55.407 --> 58:56.658
just ask my friend.

58:59.745 --> 59:02.038
Come, I'll show you what I found.

59:02.873 --> 59:03.832
Amorth!

59:03.915 --> 59:06.001
I noticed this when I first arrived.

59:12.215 --> 59:13.091
What is this?

59:14.009 --> 59:15.343
You recognize this?

59:16.261 --> 59:18.555
Yes, it's the seal
of the Spanish Inquisition.

59:18.638 --> 59:22.225
<i>Sì.</i> The darkest time
in the history of the Church.

59:23.185 --> 59:24.603
And they are...?

59:25.479 --> 59:28.440
The victims.
The ones who would not convert.

59:30.817 --> 59:32.778
There is something underneath this place.

59:33.361 --> 59:35.489
