1:02:44.761 --> 1:02:46.721
Where did you hide your key?

1:02:51.059 --> 1:02:52.394
In the stomach.

1:02:56.523 --> 1:02:57.857
Forgive me.

1:03:14.999 --> 1:03:16.167
Try this.

1:03:19.045 --> 1:03:19.879
Go.

1:03:24.342 --> 1:03:27.220
"All attempts at exorcism have failed.

1:03:27.303 --> 1:03:30.724
Satan owns this ground now.

1:03:31.349 --> 1:03:38.189
