a demon this powerful before."

1:03:49.868 --> 1:03:50.994
Gabriele.

1:03:51.077 --> 1:03:51.995
Gabriele.

1:04:00.462 --> 1:04:01.463
It worked.

1:04:01.546 --> 1:04:02.505
Ah.

1:04:04.883 --> 1:04:06.217
Thank you, my friend.

1:04:19.731 --> 1:04:20.565
Amy?

1:04:37.582 --> 1:04:40.001
