1:06:39.495 --> 1:06:40.371
Amy?

1:06:55.428 --> 1:06:57.931
"The exorcist becomes possessed himself."

1:06:58.806 --> 1:06:59.933
Friar De Ojada?

1:07:00.016 --> 1:07:03.728
You know he is the man
who convinced Queen Isabella

1:07:03.811 --> 1:07:05.688
