1:07:06.314 --> 1:07:10.360
So that means
from the time he is possessed in 1475,

1:07:10.443 --> 1:07:13.613
everything that happens after this...

1:07:14.614 --> 1:07:16.032
is the work of the devil.

1:07:17.617 --> 1:07:22.997
Centuries of persecution and torture,
the worst abuses of the Inquisition,

1:07:23.081 --> 1:07:26.501
all started by the friar
and done in the name of God

1:07:27.418 --> 1:07:28.753
by the devil.

1:07:30.338 --> 1:07:31.923
The Vatican must have known this.

1:07:32.632 --> 1:07:34.300
The Church covered it up.

1:07:34.384 --> 1:07:36.386
And they buried the truth here.

1:07:36.469 --> 1:07:39.389
"Your sins will seek you out."

1:07:39.472 --> 1:07:42.350
The construction work
must have freed the demon.

1:07:44.143 --> 1:07:45.144
Amy?

1:07:51.276 --> 1:07:52.235
Amy?

1:07:56.739 --> 1:07:57.573
Henry.

1:07:58.616 --> 1:08:00.159
- It's okay, Mommy.
- It's okay, Mommy.

1:08:00.743 --> 1:08:02.328
- Henry's okay.
- Henry's okay.

