1:08:07.292 --> 1:08:08.918
- I'm sorry, Mom.
- I'm sorry, Mom.

1:08:09.002 --> 1:08:11.671
- I don't know what got into me.
- I don't know what got into me.

1:08:12.797 --> 1:08:14.215
Well, that's okay.

1:08:15.300 --> 1:08:18.344
That's okay.
I just need your sister for a minute. Amy?

1:08:18.428 --> 1:08:20.388
- Can you forgive me, Mom?
- Can you forgive me, Mom?

1:08:31.733 --> 1:08:34.819
"The great dragon was hurled down.

1:08:34.902 --> 1:08:38.614
Hurled into the earth,
where he was bound."

1:08:38.698 --> 1:08:41.868
"And his angels with him." Revelations.

1:08:42.785 --> 1:08:46.414
Two hundred rogue angels
buried into the earth.

1:08:46.497 --> 1:08:49.959
This abbey
is one of those godforsaken places.

1:08:50.043 --> 1:08:52.462
This demon, he was trying to find them.

1:08:52.545 --> 1:08:56.257
To raise an army and destroy the Church.

1:08:56.341 --> 1:08:57.633
Amy, come here.

1:08:57.717 --> 1:08:59.886
- What's in your hand, Mommy?
- What's in your hand, Mommy?

1:09:00.803 --> 1:09:02.013
Amy, come here, right now.

1:09:02.096 --> 1:09:04.974
- What's in your hand, Mommy?
- What's in your hand, Mommy?

1:09:23.826 --> 1:09:24.952
Look.

1:09:28.289 --> 1:09:29.540
Watch me, Mommy.

1:09:29.624 --> 1:09:30.750
Watch me.

1:09:45.306 --> 1:09:46.307
His name...

1:09:48.393 --> 1:09:49.769
the king of hell...

1:09:50.937 --> 1:09:52.146
Asmodeus.

1:10:02.240 --> 1:10:03.241
Quickly!

1:10:07.912 --> 1:10:09.497
Amy, use the sedative.

1:10:18.339 --> 1:10:19.924
Tie his arms.

1:10:29.392 --> 1:10:30.726
We have his name.

1:10:39.777 --> 1:10:41.237
"Bring me the priest."

1:10:42.572 --> 1:10:43.823
What did you say?

1:10:43.906 --> 1:10:47.785
Those were the first words the demon said.
"Bring me the priest."

1:10:49.203 --> 1:10:50.580
It didn't mean me.

1:10:51.164 --> 1:10:52.540
It wants you.

1:10:52.623 --> 1:10:55.001
This demon feeds on exorcists.

1:10:55.668 --> 1:10:57.336
He had a plan once.

1:10:58.629 --> 1:11:00.465
To lure the friar here,

1:11:01.299 --> 1:11:03.759
hide amongst the righteous
and commit heinous acts

1:11:03.843 --> 1:11:05.261
in the name of God.

1:11:05.344 --> 1:11:07.555
He wants to do the same thing again.

1:11:07.638 --> 1:11:10.391
Using me to infiltrate the Church.

1:11:10.475 --> 1:11:12.685
What greater victory for the devil...

1:11:14.479 --> 1:11:17.690
than to claim the soul
of the pope's exorcist?

1:11:17.773 --> 1:11:20.568
Maybe. But we know his name now.

1:11:21.777 --> 1:11:23.988
So we have what we need to beat it

1:11:24.780 --> 1:11:26.449
and to save the child.

1:11:27.408 --> 1:11:30.536
The only thing
that can defeat us is ourselves.

1:11:33.581 --> 1:11:35.833
He will use your sins against you.

1:11:39.795 --> 1:11:41.547
I need to make confession.

1:11:42.215 --> 1:11:45.092
- To me?
- You are a priest, are you not?

1:11:47.678 --> 1:11:50.097
Forgive me, Father, for I have sinned.

1:11:51.182 --> 1:11:52.433
Trust in the Lord.

1:11:55.811 --> 1:11:57.271
I want to talk to you...

1:11:58.981 --> 1:12:01.400
about things I have confessed before...

1:12:02.777 --> 1:12:04.403
but they still burden me.

1:12:05.571 --> 1:12:07.198
In 1942...

1:12:08.533 --> 1:12:10.618
during the war, I joined the Resistance.

1:12:10.701 --> 1:12:13.329
I became a partisan
and I fought against the fascists.

1:12:15.998 --> 1:12:18.918
<i>So many of my friends
would die to German bullets.</i>

1:12:21.837 --> 1:12:22.922
<i>Why them...</i>

1:12:24.131 --> 1:12:25.550
and not me?

1:12:27.260 --> 1:12:30.096
<i>Their dead bodies
would talk to me in my dreams.</i>

1:12:31.472 --> 1:12:33.933
<i>To die in a war is heroic.</i>

1:12:34.767 --> 1:12:36.185
To survive a war...

1:12:37.603 --> 1:12:38.646
complex.

1:12:42.692 --> 1:12:43.901
<i>And then I begin to see...</i>

1:12:44.777 --> 1:12:46.529
<i>that my life had been spared.</i>

1:12:46.612 --> 1:12:49.198
<i>It was my responsibility
to give it purpose.</i>

1:12:49.282 --> 1:12:51.993
<i>And in my case, that meant to serve God.</i>

1:12:54.829 --> 1:12:59.125
In all of my years, I have tried
to embrace what is said in Matthew.

1:12:59.792 --> 1:13:04.505
<i>"What you do for the least among you,
you do for me."</i>

1:13:05.506 --> 1:13:07.216
But when it mattered...

1:13:08.926 --> 1:13:10.177
I failed.

1:13:16.017 --> 1:13:17.184
<i>I did not help her,</i>

1:13:17.268 --> 1:13:18.686
<i>I did not believe her.</i>

1:13:19.645 --> 1:13:20.813
<i>I did not listen.</i>

1:13:21.689 --> 1:13:23.858
Rosaria?

1:13:23.941 --> 1:13:25.026
Rosaria.

1:13:25.651 --> 1:13:28.738
At night, the devil fucks me.

1:13:29.322 --> 1:13:31.866
What does this devil look like?

1:13:33.951 --> 1:13:34.785
You.

1:13:44.545 --> 1:13:46.297
She was not possessed.

1:13:47.340 --> 1:13:49.216
She was mentally disturbed.

1:13:49.967 --> 1:13:54.221
<i>So I let someone else handle her case.</i>

1:13:55.264 --> 1:13:56.098
Again...

1:13:57.767 --> 1:13:59.143
my pride.

1:13:59.226 --> 1:14:00.895
I was an exorcist.

1:14:00.978 --> 1:14:03.689
The mentally disturbed, it's not my job.

1:14:05.107 --> 1:14:06.942
Do you believe me now?

1:14:07.693 --> 1:14:10.237
<i>But that all changed because of her.</i>

1:14:17.662 --> 1:14:18.621
To hear

1:14:19.580 --> 1:14:21.082
after her death

1:14:21.791 --> 1:14:25.086
the rumors of the sexual abuse,
the coverup

1:14:25.169 --> 1:14:27.630
within the walls of the Vatican City.

1:14:29.090 --> 1:14:30.549
<i>That innocent girl.</i>

1:14:32.426 --> 1:14:35.596
I did not help her when she needed me.

1:14:38.516 --> 1:14:39.684
Her soul

1:14:40.601 --> 1:14:41.936
is my burden.

1:14:43.145 --> 1:14:45.439
And this demon, he knows that.

1:14:50.236 --> 1:14:51.487
I know you...

1:14:52.863 --> 1:14:56.909
as a humble man of God, Father Amorth.

1:14:57.743 --> 1:15:00.204
It's time to lay down that burden.

1:15:01.163 --> 1:15:02.581
Forgive me, Father.

1:15:05.042 --> 1:15:07.211
I absolve you of your sins

1:15:07.294 --> 1:15:11.590
in the name of the Father,
of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit.

1:15:13.050 --> 1:15:13.884
Amen.

1:15:46.459 --> 1:15:49.503
