1:15:55.676 --> 1:15:57.386
To defeat the king of hell...

1:15:58.471 --> 1:16:00.347
we require the armor of God.

1:16:04.018 --> 1:16:05.644
To defeat the king of hell...

1:16:06.729 --> 1:16:08.522
we require the armor of God.

1:16:25.623 --> 1:16:29.835
Remember,
the demon will use your sins against you.

1:16:31.003 --> 1:16:34.965
Do not believe everything you see or hear.

1:16:36.717 --> 1:16:38.052
We have work to do.

1:16:39.929 --> 1:16:41.639
We must save this child.

1:17:16.048 --> 1:17:17.716
All done confessing?

1:17:18.300 --> 1:17:19.301
Father.

1:17:19.385 --> 1:17:22.930
Did he bare his soul to you, Tomás?

1:17:23.013 --> 1:17:26.058
Like your little whore bared her breasts?

1:17:27.685 --> 1:17:28.519
Ignore it.

1:17:29.061 --> 1:17:30.229
Pray for Henry.

1:17:30.312 --> 1:17:32.898
No amount of prayers can save Henry.

1:17:33.566 --> 1:17:35.693
Let me in, Gabriele.

1:17:35.776 --> 1:17:37.653
You know what I want.

1:17:39.321 --> 1:17:41.282
Our Father, who art in heaven...

1:17:41.365 --> 1:17:43.742
- In heaven, hallowed be thy name.
