1:18:09.727 --> 1:18:12.354
I burn in hell because of you!

1:18:12.438 --> 1:18:13.939
You are not there.

1:18:15.274 --> 1:18:17.359
You are only in my mind.

1:18:20.613 --> 1:18:23.407
- Father.
