1:18:31.290 --> 1:18:32.708
Fuck me, Tomás.

1:18:33.542 --> 1:18:36.170
- Deceiver.
- Fuck me, Tomás!

1:18:36.253 --> 1:18:37.838
- Deceiver!
- Fuck me, priest.

1:18:37.922 --> 1:18:40.341
- Oh, God.
