encounter them on every side,

1:19:38.899 --> 1:19:40.067
resist their bold attacks,

1:19:40.859 --> 1:19:43.612
and drive them hence
into the abyss of woe!

1:19:59.712 --> 1:20:00.713
Mommy?

1:20:03.132 --> 1:20:05.634
