1:21:22.336 --> 1:21:23.545
Amy.

1:21:49.404 --> 1:21:51.657
- Give me what I want!
- No!

1:21:54.493 --> 1:21:56.245
Surrender yourself to me.

1:22:07.548 --> 1:22:08.674
Julia!

1:22:25.149 --> 1:22:27.067
I told you, bitch.

1:22:27.151 --> 1:22:28.694
You're all gonna die!

1:22:28.777 --> 1:22:31.029
- Amy, please.
- Amy's gone.

1:22:32.072 --> 1:22:34.408
Julia, resist!

1:22:34.491 --> 1:22:35.701
Don't lose faith!

1:22:35.784 --> 1:22:37.995
Give me back my children!

1:22:38.078 --> 1:22:39.830
Your children are gone!

1:22:41.081 --> 1:22:42.249
Please.

1:22:42.332 --> 1:22:43.542
Amy, please.

1:22:43.625 --> 1:22:44.960
I love you.

1:22:55.053 --> 1:22:57.514
It's me you want. Let the children go.

1:22:57.598 --> 1:22:59.433
They all suffer because of you.

1:22:59.516 --> 1:23:01.768
Say the words, piggy.

1:23:05.731 --> 1:23:08.525
Be the martyr you dreamed of being.

1:23:09.151 --> 1:23:11.361
Be my piggy.

1:23:11.445 --> 1:23:12.946
Take me.

1:23:27.586 --> 1:23:28.629
Mom?

1:23:31.048 --> 1:23:33.425
No, Gabriele!

1:23:51.360 --> 1:23:52.194
Father.

1:24:00.160 --> 1:24:01.119
Mommy?

1:24:02.162 --> 1:24:03.455
What have you done?

1:24:03.538 --> 1:24:05.624
- Take the cross from my hand.
- Okay.

1:24:05.707 --> 1:24:06.583
- Take it.
- Okay.

1:24:06.667 --> 1:24:08.794
Oh, my God. Oh, my God.

1:24:08.877 --> 1:24:11.421
Oh, my God. Henry, you came back to me.

1:24:11.505 --> 1:24:12.714
- You're safe now.
- Take it!

1:24:14.508 --> 1:24:16.051
Get them out of here. Go!

1:24:16.134 --> 1:24:17.386
Hey. Hey.

1:24:17.469 --> 1:24:18.804
Julia, we have to go!

1:24:18.887 --> 1:24:20.389
- Put your arms around me.
- Let's go.

1:24:20.472 --> 1:24:22.432
Come on, run. Amy, come on.

1:24:27.354 --> 1:24:29.189
<i>Your soul is mine.</i>

1:24:39.366 --> 1:24:40.951
<i>Sullivan.</i>

1:24:41.868 --> 1:24:42.786
<i>Sullivan!</i>

1:25:04.975 --> 1:25:08.520
<i>I knew you would sacrifice yourself
to save those children,</i>

1:25:08.603 --> 1:25:10.439
<i>and now you are mine.</i>

1:25:19.531 --> 1:25:21.074
Come on. Hurry.

1:25:23.702 --> 1:25:26.246
The boy, he's safe now.
Just get away from here.

1:25:29.791 --> 1:25:31.293
- Go.
- Thank you, Father.

1:25:39.009 --> 1:25:40.510
<i>I need my pig, Gabe.</i>

1:25:49.061 --> 1:25:51.730
You will not take me.

1:25:51.813 --> 1:25:54.316
You will not take me!

1:25:54.399 --> 1:25:56.860
<i>You prideful fool.</i>

1:25:56.943 --> 1:25:59.029
<i>The friar said the exact same thing.</i>

1:26:00.197 --> 1:26:01.615
Forgive me, Lord.

1:26:04.951 --> 1:26:05.952
<i>Not yet!</i>

1:26:06.036 --> 1:26:09.414
<i>I need my pig
to get me inside the Vatican, Gabe.</i>

1:27:05.137 --> 1:27:06.388
Gabriele!

1:27:16.857 --> 1:27:18.692
Damn us both...

1:27:19.359 --> 1:27:20.986
to hell.

1:27:56.229 --> 1:27:57.355
Gabriele!

1:28:00.650 --> 1:28:01.693
Gabriele!

1:28:30.096 --> 1:28:32.265
You're too late, Tomás.

1:28:32.933 --> 1:28:36.102
He's gone, your friend. Gone.

1:28:36.686 --> 1:28:37.854
So...

1:28:40.232 --> 1:28:41.107
run along.

1:28:41.191 --> 1:28:44.694
It would be my great pleasure

1:28:44.778 --> 1:28:49.741
to excoriate your soul
and eviscerate your memory.

1:28:49.824 --> 1:28:53.119
Gabriele, listen to me. Fight it.

1:28:53.203 --> 1:28:55.205
It is just in your head.

1:28:55.288 --> 1:28:57.290
We can only be defeated by ourselves.

1:28:58.083 --> 1:28:59.626
He is not here!

1:28:59.709 --> 1:29:03.838
The little piggy is slopping
at hell's trough, where he belongs.

1:29:04.714 --> 1:29:07.676
I know you're here, Gabriele.
Pray with me.

1:29:09.594 --> 1:29:13.431
God is not here!

1:29:13.515 --> 1:29:15.725
God is always in our hearts.

1:29:15.809 --> 1:29:17.060
Focus on the prayer.

1:29:18.520 --> 1:29:19.896
"Where two of you gather...

1:29:20.897 --> 1:29:23.316
in my name, there am I."

1:29:24.109 --> 1:29:26.152
Lord, have mercy.

1:29:26.236 --> 1:29:29.072
Say it! Lord, have mercy!

1:29:33.076 --> 1:29:35.870
God is with you, Gabriele. Find him!

1:29:36.454 --> 1:29:37.831
Finish it, Tomás.

1:29:37.914 --> 1:29:39.124
Finish it!

1:29:39.207 --> 1:29:43.712
God, by your name, save me.

1:29:44.337 --> 1:29:48.592
Judge me in thy strength.

1:29:48.675 --> 1:29:51.720
O God, hear my prayer.

1:29:51.803 --> 1:29:54.848
Listen to the words of my mouth.

1:29:54.931 --> 1:29:58.393
Behold, God is my helper.

1:29:59.144 --> 1:30:00.770
<i>Give up. He is mine.</i>

1:30:00.854 --> 1:30:05.442
I adjure you
in the name of the spotless lamb.

1:30:05.525 --> 1:30:08.028
The word made flesh commands you.

1:30:08.111 --> 1:30:09.571
Asmodeus!

1:30:09.654 --> 1:30:12.574
Jesus of Nazareth commands you!

1:30:12.657 --> 1:30:17.412
And now, I adjure you in his name!

1:30:19.164 --> 1:30:21.791
Lord, heed my prayer!

1:30:21.875 --> 1:30:24.210
- Say it!
<i>- No!</i>

1:30:27.380 --> 1:30:29.674
- Gabriele.
<i>- We're not done yet.</i>

1:30:35.597 --> 1:30:38.224
<i>You're coming to hell, priests.</i>

1:30:38.975 --> 1:30:41.353
<i>I will take you both.</i>

1:30:45.899 --> 1:30:46.983
Adella.

1:31:11.132 --> 1:31:13.259
Your sins will seek...

1:31:13.343 --> 1:31:14.636
Seek you out!

1:31:14.719 --> 1:31:16.513
Tomás, use the medal!

1:31:16.596 --> 1:31:19.015
Lord, grant me the power!

1:31:29.401 --> 1:31:30.360
Gabriele!

1:31:32.904 --> 1:31:35.573
Asmodeus. In the name of the Holy Mother.

1:31:35.657 --> 1:31:39.035
See thee beneath God.

1:31:40.412 --> 1:31:42.747
See thee beneath God!

1:31:44.874 --> 1:31:47.127
Tomás! Pray the final rites.

1:31:48.586 --> 1:31:54.300
In the name of the Father,
and of the Son, and of the Holy Spirit...

1:31:55.301 --> 1:31:57.220
see thee beneath God!

1:32:18.950 --> 1:32:21.536
Gabriele, are you okay?

1:32:27.417 --> 1:32:28.460
Not so bad.

1:32:33.298 --> 1:32:35.008
- Tomás.
- What?

1:32:36.551 --> 1:32:37.969
You look like shit.

1:32:41.973 --> 1:32:43.475
Bless you, Tomás.

1:32:44.434 --> 1:32:46.060
You learned the Latin.

1:32:47.937 --> 1:32:50.648
Yes, it's similar to the Spanish.

1:32:50.732 --> 1:32:53.401
Very similar to the Spanish.

1:32:57.489 --> 1:32:58.573
Look.

1:33:03.077 --> 1:33:08.374
You know, the God,
he works in very mysterious ways.

1:33:14.214 --> 1:33:15.048
For you.

1:33:23.640 --> 1:33:26.309
Yes, he does.

1:33:35.151 --> 1:33:35.985
Cuckoo.

1:33:44.744 --> 1:33:46.246
Is that you, Gabriele?

1:33:46.830 --> 1:33:48.790
Yes, Your Holiness.

1:33:48.873 --> 1:33:51.584
And I have brought
Padre Esquibel to meet you.

1:33:51.668 --> 1:33:53.545
You look well, Your Holiness.

1:33:53.628 --> 1:33:56.214
Thanks to you both. I'm glad to see you.

1:33:57.006 --> 1:33:58.800
You had me worried this time.

1:33:59.467 --> 1:34:01.010
Sounded dangerous.

1:34:01.094 --> 1:34:02.887
Yeah, not too bad.

1:34:03.930 --> 1:34:06.558
Sometimes you fly
a little too close to the sun.

1:34:07.642 --> 1:34:09.227
It has not killed me yet.

1:34:09.310 --> 1:34:11.521
The Church will not forget
what you have done.

1:34:11.604 --> 1:34:15.400
You struck a mighty blow for our side.

1:34:15.483 --> 1:34:18.111
Saint Michael would be proud.

1:34:19.070 --> 1:34:22.282
And this is why God
put you here, Gabriele.

1:34:22.365 --> 1:34:24.367
Thank you very much, Your Holiness.

1:34:24.450 --> 1:34:28.997
And God has made a good choice
in you too, Father Esquibel.

1:34:29.080 --> 1:34:30.415
Thank you, Holy Father.

1:34:30.498 --> 1:34:35.879
The congregation
has requested a full report on Spain.

1:34:35.962 --> 1:34:37.338
A full report.

1:34:37.422 --> 1:34:42.176
So Cardinal Sullivan can tell me again
that evil only exists in my imagination?

1:34:42.260 --> 1:34:43.177
You haven't heard?

1:34:43.845 --> 1:34:47.849
Cardinal Sullivan has taken a sabbatical
in the Isle of Guam.

1:34:51.144 --> 1:34:54.063
I shall pray for Guam.

1:34:56.482 --> 1:34:59.903
And who has, uh, filled his shoes?

1:34:59.986 --> 1:35:03.823
I have found someone far more trustworthy.

1:35:05.116 --> 1:35:07.577
I will leave you in his good hands.

1:35:12.123 --> 1:35:15.126
See thee beneath God.

1:35:15.209 --> 1:35:17.086
- See thee beneath God.
- See thee beneath God.

1:35:22.008 --> 1:35:24.719
Welcome to the holiest of holies.

1:35:24.802 --> 1:35:26.512
Twelve centuries of treasures.

1:35:27.096 --> 1:35:29.599
Letters from saints and apostles.

1:35:29.682 --> 1:35:32.352
Books of wisdom and piety.

1:35:32.435 --> 1:35:34.270
Revelations of the spirit.

1:35:34.854 --> 1:35:38.399
The entire canon of Christian thought.

1:35:39.567 --> 1:35:42.195
The Vatican has purchased the abbey
from the Vasquez family

1:35:42.278 --> 1:35:44.280
and reconsecrated the soil.

1:35:44.364 --> 1:35:47.617
The family has safely relocated
back to the U.S.,

1:35:47.700 --> 1:35:49.827
where the boy made a full recovery.

1:35:54.040 --> 1:35:58.461
The friar's diary is proving very useful,
despite his abhorrence.

1:35:58.544 --> 1:36:02.882
Asmodeus has been defeated,
but there are many more to be found.

1:36:02.966 --> 1:36:08.513
Soon we will know
all of the other 199 sites on earth

1:36:08.596 --> 1:36:10.556
where God is not welcome.

1:36:11.224 --> 1:36:14.310
Gabriele, will you take on this task?

1:36:16.771 --> 1:36:21.067
This would be more
than a lifetime's work for one priest.

1:36:22.318 --> 1:36:23.653
But two priests...

1:36:25.530 --> 1:36:28.574
What do you think, Tomás?
Can you see this now as a calling?

1:36:29.200 --> 1:36:33.204
And that we must serve God
the way he wants us to serve him?

1:36:35.873 --> 1:36:37.291
Let's go to work.

1:36:40.128 --> 1:36:41.879
Let's go to hell.
